snippet.title: Quantum Derail Trailer | Physics meets comedy
snippet.description:
Quantum Derail is a point and click adventure game set in the near future in which you play as a policeman solving a physics related mystery. Play it for free at https://el-ryu.itch.io/quantumderail

The game will be available on itch.io. You can play online in your browser without flash. No downloads required.

The game is available in Enslish and Spanish.

Versión en español en: https://youtu.be/0204aTp89oY
